summary:
I have more than twelve years of experience in education and it is one of my biggest passions. I am an enthusiastic Spanish teacher who loves to learn about everything and everyone. I am interested in making a difference to people’s lives through education and a constantly motivation practice. 

I try to understand the needs of the environment and the people around me. I am a storyteller, a peace maker and a compassionate empathizer. 

I love to work on teams and I have good communicative skills to talk with others. 

I bring smiles to other people. I see the light side of things and the inner light of every person I meet.
